Package com.google.web.bindery.requestfactory.shared.jakarta

package com.google.web.bindery.requestfactory.shared.jakarta
Jakarta-specific package for server-only classes. To use these types, be sure to use the gwt-servlet-jakarta.jar, or requestfactory-server-jakarta.jar.
Since:
GWT 2.11
